          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "A trip through memory lane in a game, ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Quest for Infamy",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " was made for those who love the late 80s/early 90s PC era adventure-RPGs. It is a Sierra-style point and click adventure in the same vein as the latter half of the original ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "King’s Quest",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " series, and it’s direct inspiration, the ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
                "detail": 0,
                "format": 2,
                "mode": "normal",
                "style": "",
                "text": "Quest for Glory ",
                "type": "text",
                "version": 1
              },
              {
                "detail": 0,
                "format": 0,
                "mode": "normal",
                "style": "",
                "text": "series",
                "type": "text",
                "version": 1
              }
            ],
            "direction": "ltr",
            "format": "",
            "indent": 0,
            "type": "link",
            "rel": null,
            "target": null,
            "title": null,
            "url": "https://store.steampowered.com/app/502750/Quest_for_Glory_15/",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ". It was originally released for the PC in 2014 but it has now found its way to the Nintendo Switch. You play as William Roehm who finds himself stuck in the town of Volksville. With a regretful amount of time on his hands, he finds himself with a few mentors to choose from, and a choice of how to specialise his skills. The choice to become a brigand, a rogue, or a sorcerer is yours.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
